\[|z| = \frac{2016}{\frac{\sqrt{6} - \sqrt{2}}{2}} =\frac{4032}{\sqrt{6} - \sqrt{2}} = \frac{4032 (\sqrt{6} + \sqrt{2})}{4} = \boxed{1008 \sqrt{6} + 1008 \sqrt{2}}.\]

